18\hyphpar0\qc{....................}}}{ County.}{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qc}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{Probate No. }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{................}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{In the Estate of}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{NOTICE OF PROBATE OF WILL,}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{....................}}}{, Deceased}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{OF APPOINTMENT OF}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{EXECUTOR, AND}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{NOTICE TO CREDITORS}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{To the Department of Health and Human Services, Who May Be Interested in the Estate of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{....................}}}{, Deceased, who died on or about }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}{ (date):}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{You are hereby notified that on the }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........}}}{ day of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{(month), }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{(year), the last will and testament of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}{, deceased, bearing date of the }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........}}}{ day of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (month), }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (year) was admitted to probate in the above-named court and that }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}{ was appointed executor of the estate.}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{You are further notified that the birthdate of the deceased is }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ and the deceased\u8217\'3fs social security number is...-...-.... The name of the spouse is }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}{ The birthdate of the spouse is }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ and the spouse\u8217\'3fs social security number is...-...-...., and that the spouse of the deceased is alive as of the date of this notice, or deceased as of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{....................}}}{ (date).}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{You are further notified that the deceased was/was not a disabled or a blind child of the medical assistance recipient by the name of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}{, who had a birthdate of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{................}}}{ and a social security number of...-...-...., and the medical assistance debt of that medical assistance recipient was waived pursuant to }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 249A.53, subsection 2}}}{, paragraph }{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fa\u8221\'3f}}}{, subparagraph (1), and is now collectible from this estate pursuant to }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 249A.53, subsection 2}}}{, paragraph }{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fb\u8221\'3f}}}{.}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{Notice is hereby given that if the department of health and human services has a claim against the estate for the deceased person or persons named in this notice, the claim shall be filed with the clerk of the above-named district court, as provided by law, duly authenticated, for allowance within six months from the date of sending this notice and, unless otherwise allowed or paid, the claim is thereafter forever barred. If the department does not have a claim, the department shall return the notice to the executor with notification that the department does not have a claim within six months from the date of sending this notice.}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{Dated this }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........}}}{ day of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (month), }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (year)}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{Executor of estate}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{................................}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{Address}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{Attorney for executor}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{................................}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa80{Address}\par}{}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2001 Acts, ch 109, \'a72}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2002 Acts, ch 1119, \'a799}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2007 Acts, ch 134, \'a713}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2010 Acts, ch 1137, \'a75}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2016 Acts, ch 1073, \'a7174}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{; 2023 Acts, ch 19, \'a71276}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\fi180\ri0\li0\cbpat2{Referred to in }{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{\'a7633.410}}}{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj{, 635.13}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\sb219\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cbpat2\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{ }{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b0\fs24\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{633.305}}}{\*\bkmkstart stylerid1_2E11_2E6_2E18_2E2_2E2}{\*\bkmkend stylerid1_2E11_2E6_2E18_2E2_2E2}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\b\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{Notice if no administration.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{1.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{On admission of a will to probate without administration of the estate, the proponent shall cause to be published, in the manner prescribed in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 633.304}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, a notice of the admission of the will to probate. As soon as practicable following the admission of the will to probate, the proponent shall give notice of the admission of the will to probate by ordinary mail addressed to the surviving spouse, each heir of the decedent, and each devisee under the will admitted to probate whose identities are reasonably ascertainable, at such persons\u8217\'3f last known addresses. The notice of the admission of the will to probate shall include a notice that any action to set aside the will must be brought within the later to occur of four months from the date of the second publication of the notice or one month from the date of mailing of this notice, or thereafter be barred.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{2.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{As used in }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{this section}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{, }}}{{\i\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\u8220\'3fheir\u8221\'3f}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{ means only such person as would, in an intestate estate, be entitled to a share under }}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{section 633.219}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{3.}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{The notice shall be substantially in the following form:}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qc\fi0\ri1084\li1084{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qc}{In the District Court of Iowa}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qc\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qc\fi0\ri1084\li1084{in and for }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qc{....................}}}{ County.}{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qc}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{Probate No. }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{................}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{In the Estate of}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{NOTICE OF PROOF OF WILL}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{....................}}}{, Deceased}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{WITHOUT ADMINISTRATION}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{To All Persons Interested in the Estate of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{....................}}}{, Deceased, who died on or about }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........................}}}{ (date):}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{You are hereby notified that on the }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........}}}{ day of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (month), }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (year), the last will and testament of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{....................}}}{, deceased, bearing date of the }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........}}}{ day of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (month), }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{............}}}{ (year), was admitted to probate in the above-named court and there will be no present administration of the estate. Any action to set aside the will must be brought in the district court of the county within the later to occur of four months from the date of the second publication of this notice or one month from the date of mailing of this notice to all heirs of the decedent and devisees under the will whose identities are reasonably ascertainable, or thereafter be forever barred.}\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{Dated this }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{........}}}{ day of }{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\q